        Creates a CompositeValuesSourceConfig for this source.
        参数:
        context - The search context for this source.
        config - The ValuesSourceConfig for this source.
        pos - The position of this source in the composite key.
        numPos - The total number of positions in the composite key.
        sortField - The SortField of the index sort at this position or null if not present.
